cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.CV, cs.NE

This paper involves the development of a new model for playing a game, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves training the model using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves game theory (cs.GT) and computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with a game and its visual representation. Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) to develop the model.
